"Off → nothing recorded. Activity → metadata only (host, status, latency, swap report, leak warnings). AI request details → also captures bodies for known LLM hosts (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, Cohere, Mistral, Perplexity, x.ai, Groq, Replicate, HuggingFace). Everything → bodies for every host. Bodies are AES-GCM encrypted with the same keychain key as workspace secrets. View at App → Trace Inspector (⇧⌘I)." = "關閉 → 不記錄任何內容。活動 → 僅後設資料（主機、狀態、延遲、替換報告、洩漏警告）。AI 請求詳情 → 同時擷取已知 LLM 主機（Anthropic、OpenAI、Google、Cohere、Mistral、Perplexity、x.ai、Groq、Replicate、HuggingFace）的內容。全部 → 所有主機的內容。內容會使用與工作區機密相同的鑰匙圈金鑰進行 AES-GCM 加密。請於 App → Trace Inspector (⇧⌘I) 檢視。";
