"Block at severity:" = "封鎖嚴重等級：";
"Aggregates GitHub Advisory Database + PyPI advisories + Go's database + RubySec etc. Off by default — a low-severity CVE in a transitive subpackage shouldn't interrupt a workflow." = "彙整 GitHub Advisory Database、PyPI advisories、Go 資料庫、RubySec 等。預設關閉——傳遞相依中的低嚴重度 CVE 不應中斷工作流程。";

