"The next time “%@” launches, Bromure will offer to move its home folder onto a private ext4 disk image (with a one-time copy and a kept backup)." = "下次啟動「%@」時，Bromure 將提議把其家目錄搬移到專用的 ext4 磁碟映像檔（僅拷貝一次，並保留備份）。";
